  <brief_title>Fludarabine/Busulfan and Cyclophosphamide Conditioning for Adult ALL</brief_title>
  <official_title>Fludarabine/Busulfan and Post-infusion Cyclophosphamide as Conditioning for Adult Patients With ALL Undergoing Allogeienc Stem Cell Transplantation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
