  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  adult acute lymphocytic leukemia in 1st or second remission

          -  age 18-60 years

          -  with inform consent

          -  no contraindication for allogeneic transplantation: active infection, allergy to
             FLu/Bu/CTX, liver and renal function damage

          -  HLA matched related (6/6), unrelated donors (at least 8/10) or mismatched related
             donor (haplo)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  age less than 18 years or over 60 years

          -  liver function/renal function damage (over 2 X upper normal range)

          -  with mental disease
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
